content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 5329.34 - Responsible gaming

State Regulations

Each operator and sports pool vendor licensee shall
comply with the problem gaming, self-exclusion and excluded person requirements
set forth in Parts 5325 and 5327 of this subchapter and Part 5402 of this
subtitle. Notes
